The paper presents metrics for fairness in ranking and regression models, which are commonly studied in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses constrained optimization and robust optimization techniques, which are relevant to computational engineering (cs.CE) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
